Package ca.uwo.csd.cs2212.team06.badges

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BadgeBigMac
    The BigMac badge is earned when the user has burned over 26000 calories in their lifetime history.
    BadgeBurnedDays
    The BurnedDays badge is earned when the user has acheived their calories burned goal over a period of ten plus days.
    BadgeCat
    The Cat badge is earned if the user has been sedantary for as long as a cat is on average(16 hours).
    BadgeCircleTheGlobe
    The Circle The Globe badge is earned when the user has traveled the distance of the entire globe.
    BadgeClimbFloors
    The climbed floors badge is earned when the user has climbed th eheight of the CN tower(1815 floors).
    BadgeCustomize
    The Customize badge is earned when the user personalized their daily dashboard.
    BadgeDeathRace
    The Death Race badge is earned when the user has reached an elevation of 17000ft and has traveled 125km at a rate of 10ft/floor.
    BadgeEarlyBird
    The Early Bird badge is earned when the user is active between the times of 4am-6am.
    BadgeEndurance
    The Endurance badge is earned when the user has been very active for 60 minutes plus over a period of days.
    BadgeHeartRate
    The Heart Rate badge is earned when the user has acheived their heart rate goal for a number of days.
    BadgeMakeGoal
    The make a goal badge is earned when the user has completed one of their own personal goals.
    BadgeMitochondria
    The Mitochondria badge is earned when the user has been active for 120 plus minutes.
    BadgeMordor
    The Mordor badge is earned when the user has traveled the distance from the Shire to the Tower of Soran.
    BadgeNewYears
    The New Years badge is earned when the user is active on New Years day(Jan 1st).
    BadgeNightOwl
    The Night Owl badge is earned when the user is active late at night.
    BadgeOneStep
    The One Step badge is earned when the user has their taken first step while wearing their FitBit.
    Badges
    Used to track and manage the completion of every badge.
    BadgeSquirrel
    The Squirrel badge is earned when the user has biked at the average speed of a squirrel running.
    BadgeToInfinity
    The ToInfinity badge is earned when the user has climbed the distance it takes to get to the moon(384400000 floors).
    BadgeTriathlon
    The Triathalon badge is earned when the user has ran, biked, adn swam all in the same day.
    BadgeWorkoutDays
    The Workout Days badge is earned when the user has been active for a number of days.
